    "description": "Provenance REQ: jn7e50xjb2j4gp6b5vpjz2qw8x83t1ax\n\nRust library with TokenProvider trait (async mint/refresh/revoke) and ScopedToken struct (value, role, expires_at, metadata). Foundational primitive all consumers build on.\n\nRules:\n- NS-015: TokenProvider method signatures — async mint(role, ttl), refresh(token), revoke(token); object-safe, Send+Sync\n- NS-016: ScopedToken mandatory expiry and zeroizing type — non-optional expires_at, secrecy::SecretString, no Clone without zeroize\n- NS-017: Refresh returns new token, does not mutate — caller replaces old token\n- NS-018: Dropped futures must not leak credentials — cleanup handler if mint future dropped\n\nProvenance stats: 6 resolutions, 4 rules",
